data.description: This wonderful home was built with TLC but now could use some attention to the outside, paint and such.  You'll love the BIG kitchen offering a lot of counter space and storage. The dining area is also really big and could hold just about any size table, there is a fireplace to the far side of the room which lends itself to be a entertainment and dining area.  The master bedroom is also really big, the third bedroom is in the daylight basement as well as a huge family room. The in-ground pool is lowered partially into the ground and has a deck built around it on one side.
